commit_message: Bug fixes in the default of the input option --sample_list
removing old scripts, fixing mispelled variants, only run filtering if either genotype is running
intergrate variant filtering to the pipeline, intersect final vcf with gff of repeats, allow sample input as string and file
dictionary with input names is used in remove_duplicates so it doesn't need to search for mapped files, indexing (g)vcf files in haplotype_caller
bug fixes with check input, update input name recognision, add memoery option
added help on the qc pipeline, bug fixes on variant calling pipeline
